
fetch_action
    method = post handler for the fetch form, calls fetchdist.

fetchdist
    Local use only, assembles new release packages for upload.

fetchnew4
    Fetch script from wrcad.com, for uploading.

update
update_help
update_man
    Scripts from wrcad.com used to automate uploading of new
    distribs.

wr_filename
    print distrib file name, args: program osname version

wr_install
    For export (direct from web site).  User must use this to install
    programs, for SafeInstall feature.

    Also used as installation script for internal install command. 
    copied to startup directories.

